  <summary date="2021-11-23T21:09:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Prevent Taliban Support Act

This bill prohibits using federal funds to provide any kind of support to the Taliban or a Taliban affiliate. It also prohibits waiving any U.S.-imposed sanctions on the Taliban or a Taliban affiliate unless a law is enacted specifically providing for such a waiver.</summary>
